actions.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

official_title: A bill to extend until January 1, 1995, the existing suspension of duty on (6R,7R)-7-((R)-2-Amino-2-phenylacetamido)-3-methyl-8-oxo-5-thia-1-azabicyclo(4.2.0)oct-2-ene-2-carboxylic acid disolvate.

summary.text: Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1994, the suspension of duty on (6R, 7R)-7-((R)-2-amino-2-phenylacetamido)-3- methyl-8-oxo-5-thia-1-azabicyclo(4,2,) oct-2-ene-2-carboxylic acid disolvate.
